  "description": "Generation convergence, trigger backlog, stale-answer causes, and queue freshness for hosted Eshu. Uses only bounded eshu_runtime_* and eshu_dp_* metrics. No private repo names, trigger payloads, delivery IDs, or provider secrets appear as labels.",
